parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoOp.What the hell is all this stuff?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.Looks like a storage room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoOp.What a pack rat.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlOp.This stuff looks valuable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx.Let’s take something!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Don’t touch anything Tasha. We’re only here for clues.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoDe.I don’t want Sofia knowing anyone was here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaOp.What’s this thing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.It looks like a Tikpak headdress...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.And this here is a Tikpak shaman staff.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaOp.How do you know?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I found this staff under Estero Key.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Sofia is studying the Tikpak. It’s why she claims to be here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrOp.How much is it worth?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Not sure. But I think there’s something a lot bigger to be found here than she is letting on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.Clare seems to know a lot about the Tikpak. It must be why Sofia hired her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaOp.What is it that they want?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoDe.It's nothing... Just some pirate treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaHaOp.Damn! I want some pirate booty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Uhhh... It’s not much... Maybe a couple hundred thousand dollars worth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.Sofia hired a treasure hunter to collect a hundred grand?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.Do I look stupid 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Tasha! You’re going to get me into trouble.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaEx.Come on 1Hero. I helped you break into this place. You have to tell me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.I can’t. It involves some very dangerous people.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrOp.I like danger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.Don’t push it Tasha. Just let it go.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.It’s obvious 1Hero. It’s a giant stash of treasure and I want in on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.God damn it Tasha. The people we’re selling the treasure to... They killed my father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaShAg.Holy shit! We have to fuck them up!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.I know... And I’m working on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrEx.I want to fuck them up with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.You have to lay low Tasha. It’s not going to be simple.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.I have to find the treasure before I can do anything else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrOp.So you’re going to meet these assholes with the promise of treasure...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaHaAg.And then shoot them all!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.No! It’s not like that. I can’t tell you anything more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaOp.Aww. Come on 1Hero. You don’t want to keep me in the dark do you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.Sorry Tasha. It’s for your own good.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.You think I can’t handle myself? You have no idea who I am.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.This is serious Tasha.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.I’ve dealt with some really bad people in my life 1Hero. I can handle this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.What are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.I was part of a gang... Sort of.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Really? You’re a gangster?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.No! It’s not like that... I may have robbed a few places when I was younger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeShOp.Really!? Did you get away with it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnOp.Hell no! But I was just a kid... So I got off easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaDe.Can’t say the same for my Mom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeShOp.Your Mom was with you!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnEx.With me? She was the brains of our operation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaDe.I haven't seen her in 10 years.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.I’m sorry to hear that Tasha.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaEx.I know what it’s like to be in danger 1Hero. You don’t have to worry about me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.I’ve been told not to tell anyone. You know, if word gets out about the treasure it’ll make it a lot harder to find.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaOp.Don’t make me beg 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.You know. For someone who makes fun of treasure hunting you sure have changed your tune.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx.I was wrong about you 1Hero. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Can I trust you Tasha?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlOp.Of course.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.Take her away. I must speak with him alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaMaAg.Hey! Where are you taking me?!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Sofia. You must believe me. We came here to learn what we could about the Tikpak.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.You’re that desperate to help me in my pursuit? I doubt that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeShEx.Sofia! The Tikpak survived. They became the Cape Vedra natives!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.You’re not telling me anything I don’t already know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.But I suspect you have little interest in the Tikpak culture.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp.No... You’re here for something else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.What good is the Tikpak to you Sofia? Clearly you’re looking for the treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.So naive. The Treasure of Nadia is a children’s fairy tale.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.I’m willing to bet that it’s not.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.I do not seek treasure 1Hero. I have all the money I’ll ever need.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.You however are the son of a reckless man who only cared about fame.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.And you’re telling me that you care about something more?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.A perspective you’d never understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.I’m betting my life on that treasure Sofia. I know it’s real.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnEx.You’re young and arrogant 1Hero. You won't die for an imaginary treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.I will if I don’t find that treasure. The Eclipse Guild is after me now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaDe.A gift from your Father?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.I’m going to avenge his death.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaDe.You’re braver than I thought to be making deals with the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp.Even I know to keep my distance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.You’ve never dealt with them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.I’m above that 1Hero. I made my wealth without lowering myself to black market dealings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.Don’t make your problems mine 1Hero. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.If you’re here for clues I assure you that your search is in vain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaDe.You will not find the treasure of Nadia.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp.Perhaps your best course of action is to disappear. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.I won’t run Sofia. I have my own plans. And part of that plan is to find the Tikpak treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.You’ve got a strong spirit 1Hero. And a willingness to take risks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlDe.I admire that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnEx.I’m afraid one of my own may have the same desire for treasure as you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.Perhaps you’d be of use to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What are you saying Sofia?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlEx.If you help me. I will pay your debt to the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeShOp.You want me to spy on Clare?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.You know her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.She worked with my Father and I know she’s working for you. Along with those two thugs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnEx.She’s gone rogue. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnDe.She’s operating behind my back, wasting my money.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaEx.I need an expert on the Tikpak culture. I need someone I can trust.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.Find what I need and I will make your problems go away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Then tell me what I need to know. Don’t make me guess.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaEx.Clare is an expert on the Tikpak culture. Follow her. Learn from her moves.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp.She seeks the treasure, but there is something else to be found.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.What is it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlEx.The key to unlocking the Tikpak language.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Why does that matter?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.The language of the Tikpak shamans holds supernatural abilities.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlEx.The discovery would change the world.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.You believe in that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp.Perhaps my efforts are fruitless. But I am willing to take that risk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.So, you trust me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.You want more than money 1Hero. I can see it in your soul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlEx.Your desire to please your lost Father can be my benefit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.Clare has lost her way. She’s wasting my time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlEx.Look beyond the lust for wealth and use her knowledge to find the true prize.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.Do you have what it takes 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.I can’t say I believe that a language can be magic. But your offer is pretty hard to turn down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.You don’t have to believe it. Just find me the clues I need to finish what I’ve started.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Let Tasha and I go, and I’ll find what it is you’re looking for.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoFlOp.That’s the spirit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaShAg.What the hell 1Hero?! Run!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoMaAg.Get back here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp>.Wait!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoBaOp>.Let her go.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaOp.As you wish Madam.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.Leave 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SoAnOp.Don’t let me down.");
